            "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2047476386/image_2047476386.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"View from above of Amazon prime cardboard carton package\" data-id=\"2047476386\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"698px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2047476386/image_2047476386.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2047476386/image_2047476386.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2047476386/image_2047476386.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2047476386/image_2047476386.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2047476386/image_2047476386.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2047476386/image_2047476386.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2047476386/image_2047476386.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2047476386/image_2047476386.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">AdrianHancu</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>My last article on e-commerce giant Amazon.com, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMZN\" title=\"Amazon.com, Inc.\">AMZN</a></span>), in December 2024, was titled \"<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743009-amazon-further-rise-likely-but-look-out-for-the-challenges\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743009-amazon-further-rise-likely-but-look-out-for-the-challenges\" target=\"_blank\">Further Rise Likely, But Look Out For The Challenges</a>\". Up to early February, the price did inch up a bit. But that's about it. Since then, the</p>",
